{"tid":359925,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Freistatt 感化院","createTime":"2017-08-15T00:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T03:03:53.000Z","uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"689ad9957b3540e298870c2c1808305e098b1698","tid":359925,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:48:47.000Z","msg":"這部電影根據真實歷史改編，將德國社會的壓抑和青春的反叛結合起來，展現出了德國文明的另一種方式&mdash;&mdash;青少年矯正機構。這類型的電影並不少見，並且模式也大致相同，個人成長和社會經歷結合在一起，將制度的不完善，對自由的禁錮，對尊嚴的踐踏等等描述的非常到位。儘管《感化院》是一部非常虐心的電影，但是，其中飽含著一個民族的反思，而這也是德國電影最獨特的地方。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/7JKGjm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2F7JKGjm.html&d=5r9K3LpCLxi7ws6UocUQQTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=68cf24a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/7JKGjm.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/084822_8bff6fd12226cd734dfd38129c7cce4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F084822_8bff6fd12226cd734dfd38129c7cce4e.jpg&h=0e5a0b40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13a8b1b20a3fe2d2c65d00284903bcdf6e95e2d9","tid":359925,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76db11db8942087188d429aaa1eb96030a1b254b","tid":359925,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"難得有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}